Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:37.41,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want him to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:40.12,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:46.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:50.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Morita-san went to America?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't know when he's coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And his room is filled with Matsumoto meters?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.89,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a reference to Leiji Matsumoto's Galaxy Express 999.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:02.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I still can't believe it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he going to do in America?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:05.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Study? Work as a foreign laborer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Morita-san even speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only interested in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:17.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I put it into words, the reality of the\Nsituation wore off more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And even I started wondering if this was really happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Morita-san really go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Without telling us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:36.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he suddenly went off to America and\Nwe don't even know when he's coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:44.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he did disappear randomly a lot,\Nso maybe this is expected of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his tuition and visa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:51.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to pay rent to our landlord\Nin person. What will he do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his notice of absence for school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I guess he might not need one since\Nhe only has his graduate thesis left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:05.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't gather anything from the expression\Non her small and still feverish face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:10.21,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want him to come back? Or do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that was supposed to mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he ask me something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:21.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Morita-san come back right away\Nif I told him that I wanted him to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:26.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, that question isn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, do you want Morita-san to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takemoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what good will asking her that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:40.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:53.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's good to keep trying until you've\Ntried everything you've wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:05.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of response did I want from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:12.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her response wasn't that of a delicate girl in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was more straightforward, more powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and clearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:36.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice that Hagu-chan liked Morita-san at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived with her for a year and didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I make of my slowness as a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:50.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's one of your good points, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:53.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:57.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that you're just saying that I'm insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about sensitivity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:05.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm not going to help you make your pottery anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I think it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. But this is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:16.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A construction design office even needs to obtain the ceramics\Nthat will be displayed in a restaurant's lobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when we take on the entire project like this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fun... and educational.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:30.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up are two beige-colored 38 cm ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be big, so we should make them by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These things would be pretty expensive if we had to buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:42.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to ply money from them to pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll apologize beforehand if we end up paying you with items.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Paying with items? What would I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a small fountain that's no longer being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a large table for a model room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a replica of Venus de Milo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask for anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:08.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can ask for anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'd wish for Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to get money for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:24.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If Hagu-chan has been thinking about Morita-san\Nbut hasn't realized that it's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd like to just leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:35.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since depending on how you look at it, it might also mean that she\Ndoesn't have the mental capacity to consider a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of everything, we're talking about Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:45.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he tears anyone who gets serious about him to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:45.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord2.5\be1\shad0\fs44\fscy80\3c&HECF3F4&\c&H6A6A67&}stress
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love sure is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of pisses me off when you say it, Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, I'm sorry. I really might've stepped\Non something I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're apologizing pisses me off even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:10.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Ramen! How about the one from Tenka Ippin? I'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:22.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is like a runaway train with his overflowing talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been enlightened regarding the fact\Nthat it's best for us to let him do as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:30.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But America all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That man doesn't pay attention to anything other people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:43.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... he really paid attention to your works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:49.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "I've never seen anyone but\Nmyself make something that huge."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:02.30,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nandaka dou demo yoku natte gozen chuu sabotte shimatta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:02.30,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't really care, so I skipped the morning classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:07.89,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}miesuita iiwake wo shitara yokei meittekita
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:07.89,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Making poor excuses just made me more depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:14.52,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kinou no yoru kanojo ga tabeta poteto chippusu no fukuro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:14.52,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The bag of chips she was eating last night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:20.40,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}terebi wo minagara nondeta biiru mo sono mama teeburu ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:20.40,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and the beer she was drinking while watching the TV are still on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:26.61,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}saenai hibi da to wa omou
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:26.61,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These days feel pretty dull to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:32.83,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ironna koto kangaechairu kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:32.83,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}though I think about various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:39.29,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"denwa kurai yokose" to kazoku wa iu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:39.29,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My family says, "Can't you at least call?",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:46.17,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hanaseru koto wa betsu ni nani mo nai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:46.17,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I don't really have anything to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:51.72,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"tsumaranai" to yoku kanojo wa iu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:51.72,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She says, "I'm bored" a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:59.27,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mou sugu shougo sorosoro ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:59.27,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's almost noon, I guess I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:02.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:15.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her back as she poured all her heart into working on the canvas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:21.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san's back as he was swinging\Nthe wood pick alone that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both in a world I can't enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:30.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And... distance doesn't exist in that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... What kind of response did I want from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:47.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have her brawl like usual and say\Nthat she wants him to come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been far, far better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:03.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I planted basil and beafsteak plants on my\Nbalcony in the beginning of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They grew quickly under the summer sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:12.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But during one of the July typhoons, the tallest beefsteak plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...snapped in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:19.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother looked at the snapped beefsteak plant and said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:24.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"That won't return to normal, so tear it off where it broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:29.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, a new stem will grow from\Nthere and new leaves will grow from it."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:34.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't help but hesitate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:40.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the small leaves on the\Nend of the stem were still healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:45.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't change at all after the stem snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:10:58.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Teakettle: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Hamabi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:14.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't she... kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...becoming more manly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wonderful, Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:28.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a hard time believing that the person\Nwho drew this is right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if these are the cherry blossoms from this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones we all saw at the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:40.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that all the cherry blossoms she's\Nseen in her life are meshed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though we were all looking\Nat the same cherry blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:43.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\i1\shad0\bord0\frz15\fscy90\fs32\move(705,373,662,373)\frx10\fry4\c&H7587B0&}Modern Art
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:48.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...they looked like this in Hagu-chan's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:52.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke that huge squeegee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in your body does such monstrous strength reside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:09.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Have some tea and donuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Hagu-chan, did you wash your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:18.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not working with clay today, so it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Let's go see the fireworks, Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:35.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put on yukata and geta, dress up, and eat caramel apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:35.28,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Yukata: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a type of kimono worn in the summer; {\3c&H635514&\be0}Geta: {\be1\3c&H000000&}wooden sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukata... fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my house. We'll lend you a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:51.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be by the riverbank tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sudden, but I wonder if Mayama-san will also make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask him quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu's ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this Mayama-san? Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't Mayama busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:03.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It starts around 7:30 or 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:05.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not be able to come. Um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, you're spilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A party to celebrate the end of a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A mahjong tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:15.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess it won't work out, then. I'll\Ninvite you again some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, you're spilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear that you're busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:24.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You don't need to go through all that trouble to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:30.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. We're all having fun over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At 8:00! No, I'll be there by 7:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me on my cell phone. I'll\Nbe near the bridge by the levee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:43.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama says that he's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Hagumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.94,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H64&\3a&H64&\frz5\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs30\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\i1\3c&HBCDCE9&\c&H4486DF&\pos(619,386)\frx10\fry7}Yamada\NLiquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Aunt Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She runs a kimono store in Kouenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hanamoto Hagumi. I'll be in your care today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. She really is small, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now which one shall we wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:08.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... How about this one for you, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:11.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Which one should I choose? This is nice. Oh, but that's nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:11.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that a little too mature, Aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:17.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that's a little mature fits girls your age perfectly.
