Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:27.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a man or two you want to emasculate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:24.39,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\frz10\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fsp2\fscy80\fs42\bord1.5\be1\pos(482,302)\c&H7E9E65&\3c&H3F5047&}Jade\N{\fs25\fscy95}(extra-large)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:24.76,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\frz10\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fsp2\fscy80\fs42\bord1.5\be1\pos(482,302)\c&H7E9E65&\3c&H3F5047&}Jade\N{\fs25\fscy95}(extra-large)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to go with this, Aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then I'll go with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want to go with the sexy look, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's do our best, Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:42.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you two need to go take a bath first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:52.12,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H64&\3a&H64&\frz5\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs30\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\i1\3c&HBCDCE9&\c&H4486DF&\pos(619,386)\frx10\fry7}Yamada\NLiquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put on your yukata afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go cleanse your bodies and get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes'm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.33,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fsp4\be1\shad0\fad(1000,0)\fs65\fscx65\3c&H6C5E55&\c&HA89386&\pos(409,322)}30 minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:14:59.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:03.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to be fixated on the flower stems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:12.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See, even if you choose one with good designs,\Nit'll match as long as the color does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.85,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this, we'll pull out our last stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:19.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go borrow the one we made two years\Nago for Kayo-chan from the sushi restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:22.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukata...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:26.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait. I'm sure that I'll turn you into a real beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, we'll start with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:34.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aunt Aki, do I really have to wrap this around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:41.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have ample breasts, so if you don't put\Nthat on, they'll sit prominently on the obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:41.97,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Obi: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a wide belt worn with a kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to wrap the towel around\Nyou, would you rather put this bra on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:49.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. This isn't romantic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:52.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're planning to take it off today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. Your aunt is so inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no such plans! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wrap it! I just need to wrap it around me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:04.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't need to wrap it around\Nyourself. You don't have any curves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:08.41,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H64&\frz5\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs30\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\i1\frx10\fry17\frx10\fry7\pos(626,386)\c&H305DAC&\3c&H5FB4F1&}Yamada\NLiquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a little too mature-looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you look wonderful, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See, that says it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu! You're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:27.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I guess the problem is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbon obi and a goldfish pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:33.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, it's for an elementary school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:34.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukata...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:40.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. What's her problem? It fits\Nher so well that it's almost scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, you look cute! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:50.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this to sell at the store, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll lend you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hairpin I made from an obi stopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu! What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:09.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Goldfish! Goldfish! Butterfly! Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:12.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, the main problem is the fact that it fits you that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:12.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute! Cute! Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to wear what fits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:18.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:21.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're going to see the fireworks, Ayu?
