Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ayu and Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukata, huh? That's nice.
