Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, you look cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, take this roll sushi with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we got a lot of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, you're amazing! You're so popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:56.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:17:58.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Yamada-san and Hagu-chan. You're both really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama called and said that he'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from a man who hates being left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this really, really look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird? Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I look weird with my forehead showing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really looks good on you, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's Mayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:47.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You came early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I skipped out on the mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san, Mayama-san's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:01.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:09.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you have a lot of luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I'll carry it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.84,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to hear just those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I put my hair up, chose my kimono, went\Nthrough a heck of a time getting dressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wore geta that I'm not used to wearing,\Nand got my heart pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:14.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All for those words from no one but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:22.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that maybe your heart would tilt just a little bit towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu... what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:32.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always end up dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:38.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over, never getting tired of it, like\Na fool repeating the only thing he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went out on the balcony a few days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:50.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,the snapped beefsteak plant was writhing on\Nthe ground, unable to hold up its own weights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like my mom said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:57.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to tear it off where it snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:04.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no choice but to break it\Nthere and let it grow a new stem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:09.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still become hopelessly confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to break this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:15.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to break...
